00:11:46.400 --> 00:11:50.800
Unfortunately, the soldier steps over it and&nbsp;
prepares to shoot Steve. Brianna disappears,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:50.800 --> 00:11:55.200
and a massive explosion rocks Steve and the&nbsp;
soldier. The soldier loses balance and steps on&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:55.200 --> 00:11:59.360
the landmine, exploding him to pieces. Steve&nbsp;
rises to his feet and sits on the boulder.

